ref="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Gi%C3%A1c-L%C3%A2m-Vi%C3%AAn-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/poem-kp7DN8K06nyl-WY1FE15IA">Tặng Giác Lâm Viên Quang thiền sư - 贈覺林圓光禪師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Ti%E1%BB%81n-X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-ph%C3%BA/poem-me7U_8vSr2qqarH3OBVAMw">Tiền Xích Bích phú - 前赤壁賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-V%C4%83n/Xu%C3%A2n-khu%C3%AA-o%C3%A1n/poem-dvHqjVJsX1YLXCNIcOPAvA">Xuân khuê oán - 春閨怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-V%C4%83n/author-ZTPl84jecbQSzBLzfpukRQ">Trình Trường Văn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
